(---) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(## Overview) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(In the OVOS ecosystem, the messagebus is implemented as a **WebSocket** interface. Messages) Tj
T*
(follow a structured format containing:) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(- A `type`: identifying the intent or action) Tj
T*
(- An optional `data` payload \(JSON\)) Tj
T*
(- An optional `context` dictionary for session or routing metadata) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(Some messages trigger actions; others act as notifications or state broadcasts. Both core OVOS) Tj
T*
(components and external systems \(e.g., [HiveMind]\(https://jarbashivemind.github.io/HiveMind-) Tj
T*
(community-docs\)\) can interact with the bus.) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(---) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(## Configuration) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(The messagebus is configured in `mycroft.conf` under the `websocket` section:) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(```json) Tj
T*
("websocket": {) Tj
T*
(    "host": "127.0.0.1",) Tj
T*
(    "port": 8181,) Tj
