() Tj
T*
(Each message sent on the bus consists of:) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(```json) Tj
T*
({) Tj
T*
(    "type": "message.type",) Tj
T*
(    "data": { /* arbitrary JSON payload */ },) Tj
T*
(    "context": { /* optional metadata */ }) Tj
T*
(}) Tj
T*
